                        INFORMATION
         Open Source Software used in the SE Harmony Hub node

The SE Harmony Hub node contains, among other things, Open Source Software files,
as specified below, developed by third parties and licensed under an Open Source
Software license. These Open Source Software files are protected by copyright. 
Your right to use the Open Source Software is governed by the relevant applicable
Open Source Software license conditions.

